{"tid":1956570,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"小弟開左個日常用品嘅格價IG","createTime":"2020-04-03T09:11:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-05T15:44:50.000Z","uid":106387,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4a3ce0069106efe38c82adb9f0a3050ee0cb8002","tid":1956570,"uid":106387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T09:11:32.000Z","msg":"話說小弟因為疫情 比人炒左<br />\n呢排除左做步兵搵返2餐之外<br />\n發現都要諗下點樣洗少D錢<br />\n跟住認真留意下平時日常用品D價格<br />\n發現真係可以差好遠下<br />\n所以小弟就開左個IG 專Po 日常用品 邊到買最平 邊隻包裝最抵買<br />\n希望幫到自己 又幫到大家<br />\n暫時PO 左D零食 ONLY<br />\n大家見到咩產品平嘅話可以話我知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我會盡快更新<br />\nIG: pricemasterhk<br />\n個IG 新開0 follower 希望大家幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就黎要窮到要食樹皮了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77046a3c9e98fbb6a1efc8b4fad9eefb19e66796","tid":1956570,"uid":16061,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T09:28:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www3.consumer.org.hk/pricewatch/supermarket/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww3.consumer.org.hk%2Fpricewatch%2Fsupermarket%2F&d=HDFqBNw8TQCe%2BIc9lyi2Bs2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=543d6692\" target=\"_blank\">https://www3.consumer.org.hk/pricewatch/supermarket/</a>"},{"pid":"3fd8578c17084022c5129b849ef4098d359683b6","tid":1956570,"uid":106387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77046a3c9e98fbb6a1efc8b4fad9eefb19e66796","tid":1956570,"uid":16061,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T09:28:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www3.consumer.org.hk/pricewatch/supermarket/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww3.consumer.org.hk%2Fpricewatch%2Fsupermarket%2F&d=HDFqBNw8TQCe%2BIc9lyi2Bs2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=543d6692\" target=\"_blank\">https://www3.consumer.org.hk/pricewatch/supermarket/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime